Round: Round 9:
[Jan 4, 1920]
Huracán (BUE)           1:0  Estudiantes LPG
Boca Juniors            abd  Sportivo de Almagro    [abandoned at 4:0]
[Jan 16, 1920]
Boca Juniors            4:0  Sportivo de Almagro    [awarded]

[Jan 21, 1920]
The Association put an end to the championship because the tournament took 
longer than expected. 
Fourteen matches were not played. 
So, Boca Juniors ended up in the first position.   

* 1. Boca Juniors             7    7    0    0    27     5   14 Champion
* 2. Estudiantes LPG          8    3    1    4    10     7    7
* 3. Huracán (BUE)            5    2    0    3     3    11    4
* 4. Eureka                   4    1    1    2     5     6    3
* 5. Sportivo de Almagro      4    1    1    2     3     8    3
* 6. Porteño                  6    1    1    4     5    16    3

