Racing Club won the championship in this round with the following line-ups:

Tigre:       Guilliermo Magistretti; Constante Bernasconi, Blase Casildo Vitale;
             Rodolfo L. Bruzzoni, Félix Cristóbal, Fermín Sernich; Adolfo 
             Heisinger, Juan Manuel Dattas, R. Suria, M. González, José V. 
             González.

